{"tid":748134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"ofo傳撤大部分美國業務","createTime":"2018-07-19T03:29:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-19T04:39:05.000Z","uid":141151,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"287df7d04cfe92b99970d67698f28e1a914a31ae","tid":748134,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T03:29:01.000Z","msg":"ofo傳撤大部分美國業務<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/china/article/1894048\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fchina%2Farticle%2F1894048&d=5yHp%2FArRmvewwdqCqKTArNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=4a598d22\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/china/article/1894048</a><br />\n<br />\n內地共享單車巨頭ofo傳將關閉大部分美國業務。<br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》引述消息人士透露，ofo進入美國市場不足一年後，計劃關閉大部分美國業務，並裁減美國大多數的員工，撤回到少數幾個大城市。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，ofo仍在考慮保留哪些城市的業務。最近數周至少有3名ofo美國業務高層離職，其中包括北美業務負責人。<br />\n<br />\n目前ofo在美國30多個市場投放超過4萬輛單車。"},{"pid":"9ccca4f8012679b69d94a496971e26e5753c8693","tid":748134,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T03:30:54.000Z","msg":"哩招夠晒仆街<br />\n4萬架垃圾隨街拋棄"},{"pid":"01e58f534f02ecb6a448d66134f386179c5e1788","tid":748134,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T03:30:59.000Z","msg":"最撚憎呢堆共享坑爹，阻撚住晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc39a2cfecbf10fd9893054cf7d50fd603d1dc7e","tid":748134,"uid":160662,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T03:33:43.000Z","msg":"其實水已CAP, 乜柒天使基金去到E輪咁滯, 幾十億美金袋袋平安"},{"pid":"3bcc53078a2f0e00f5fdfa2d04f025eef8d310c0","tid":748134,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T03:34:01.000Z","msg":"不如撤左香港先啦<br />\n<br />\n阻撚住晒, 影響市容！"},{"pid":"50967f5fbc1ddbe21b77ae9cef2c37078f502e46","tid":748134,"uid":49812,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"3bcc53078a2f0e00f5fdfa2d04f025eef8d310c0","tid":748134,"uid":79563,"like":1,"disl